fulltitle: Quincy Jones: Guitar Center Sessions - Thriller
title: Quincy Jones: Guitar Center Sessions - Thriller
description: On December 4th 2010 at Guitar Center Hollywood, Host Nic Harcourt sat down with musician, producer, and conductor Quincy Jones during a very special edition of Guitar Center Sessions. Quincy has won 27 Grammy Awards, and worked with artists such as Duke Ellington, Frank Sinatra, Ludacris, Michael Jackson, Usher, and many more. Join us as Quincy discusses his celebrated career, shares his new album Soul Bossa Nostra along with his book Q On Producing.
